{"tid":4580,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人可以入黎俾啲建議我","createTime":"2016-11-26T14:27:19.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-27T14:22:52.000Z","uid":11230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"74de5c489a0b5f8a9342564357ff53f83db54fb3","tid":4580,"uid":11230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T14:27:19.000Z","msg":"我join左一個出面搞既日文interest course，得2堂既<br />\n咁係堂入面就有一個女仔我覺得幾有好感，<br />\n係好到我覺得好想同佢發展落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申少少我拍過一次拖，同ex一齊左幾年，分左手一年，之後我都無鐘意過人，因為我鐘意啲type 有啲特別（要係乖既女仔），今次好難得竟然俾我再遇到一個我覺得岩我既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到琴日俾我發現原來佢係同我同一間公司，但係唔同team所以之前一直唔知（唔同層），但問開同事原來佢resign 左一個月琴日都係佢既last day <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n由係個course 見到佢到發現係同公司個下真係打從心底覺得好開心，但知左佢last day 之後就跌左去谷底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今次好想再認真拍多次拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 宜家應該點做好<br />\n<br />\n我同佢其實無認真傾過計，只係大家知大家係邊個<br />\n我已經問人拎左佢電話同ig ，但係貿貿然搵佢又好奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唉我應該點做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"180bebe05c96bff55cdfd3f6d15647b6f9c95453","tid":4580,"uid":23322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T14:31:11.000Z","msg":"可以經fb扮晒因為同公司同有mutual friend再同佢msg下先，有啲共同野，值得一試喎！支持你巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"090ac88662b73f6622379ca598337013e0f6c0ca","tid":4580,"uid":11230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T15:36:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可以經fb扮晒因為同公司同有mutual friend再同佢msg下先，有啲共同野，值得一試喎！支持你巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br /